data.name: ReadDebtDebtDetail
data.value: select T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.OB_TRN_ID, T1.OB_TRN_TYP, T1.CREATED_TMST, T1.CSP_SUP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_SUP_TYPE, T1.OTY_TYPE, T2.DUE_DT, T2.BAL_DUE_AMT, T2.RETIRED_DT, T2.CVRD_PRD_START_DT, T2.PRECNVRSN_PGM_CD, T2.CREATED_TMST from CKT_OB_TRN T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_DEBT_DTL T2 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.OTY_TYPE = T2.OTY_TYPE) and (T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T2.OBG_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.OB_TRN_TYP = T2.OTR_TYPE) and (T1.OB_TRN_ID = T2.OTR_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.CPA_TYPE = T2.CPA_TYPE) and (T1.CSP_NUMBER = T2.CSP_NUMBER) and (T2.CREATED_TMST <= @createdTmst) and (T1.CPA_SUP_TYPE is not null) and (@cspSupNumber = T1.CSP_SUP_NUMBER) and (@otyType = T1.OTY_TYPE) and (@obgGeneratedId = T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID) and (@cspNumber = T1.CSP_NUMBER) and (@cpaType = T1.CPA_TYPE) and (T1.CREATED_TMST <= @createdTmst)

data.name: ReadLegalActionDetailLegalAction1
data.value: select distinct top(1) T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER, T1.LA_DETAIL_NO, T1.END_DT, T1.EFFECTIVE_DT, T1.CREATED_TSTAMP, T1.NON_FIN_OBLG_TYPE, T1.DETAIL_TYPE, T2.CLASSIFICATION, T2.FILED_DT, T2.STANDARD_NO, T2.CREATED_TSTAMP from CKT_LEGAL_ACTION T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_LEG_ACT_CAS_RL T3 with(readuncommitted) on (T2.LEGAL_ACTION_ID = T3.LGA_ID) and (@croIdentifier1 = T3.CRO_IDENTIFIER) and (@croType1 = T3.CRO_TYPE) and (@cspNumber1 = T3.CSP_NUMBER) and (@casNumber1 = T3.CAS_NUMBER) and (T2.CLASSIFICATION in ('J', 'O')) and (T2.FILED_DT > @filedDt) and (T2.CREATED_TSTAMP <= @createdTstamp) join CKT_LEG_ACT_CAS_RL T4 with(readuncommitted) on (T2.LEGAL_ACTION_ID = T4.LGA_ID) and (@croIdentifier2 = T4.CRO_IDENTIFIER) and (@croType2 = T4.CRO_TYPE) and (@cspNumber2 = T4.CSP_NUMBER) and (@casNumber2 = T4.CAS_NUMBER) join CKT_LEGAL_ACT_DTL T1 with(readuncommitted) on (T2.LEGAL_ACTION_ID = T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER) and (T1.CREATED_TSTAMP <= @createdTstamp) and (T1.DETAIL_TYPE = 'N') and (T1.NON_FIN_OBLG_TYPE in ('HIC', 'ZCS', 'UM')) order by T1.NON_FIN_OBLG_TYPE desc

data.name: ReadLegalActionDetailLegalAction2
data.value: select distinct T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER, T1.LA_DETAIL_NO, T1.END_DT, T1.EFFECTIVE_DT, T1.CREATED_TSTAMP, T1.NON_FIN_OBLG_TYPE, T1.DETAIL_TYPE, T2.CLASSIFICATION, T2.FILED_DT, T2.STANDARD_NO, T2.CREATED_TSTAMP from CKT_LEGAL_ACTION T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_LEGAL_ACT_DTL T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_LEGAL_ACT_PERS T3 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.LA_DETAIL_NO = T3.LAD_R_NUMBER) and (T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER = T3.LGA_R_IDENTIFIER) and (T3.ACCOUNT_TYPE = 'R') and (@cspNumber1 = T3.CSP_NUMBER) and (T1.CREATED_TSTAMP <= @createdTstamp) and (T1.DETAIL_TYPE = 'F') join CKT_LEGAL_ACT_PERS T4 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.LA_DETAIL_NO = T4.LAD_R_NUMBER) and (T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER = T4.LGA_R_IDENTIFIER) and (T4.ACCOUNT_TYPE = 'S') and (@cspNumber2 = T4.CSP_NUMBER) on (T2.LEGAL_ACTION_ID = T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER) and (T2.CLASSIFICATION in ('J', 'O')) and (T2.FILED_DT > @filedDt) and (T2.CREATED_TSTAMP <= @createdTstamp)

data.name: ReadObligationTypeObligation
data.value: select T1.DEBT_TYP_ID, T1.DEBT_TYP_CD, T1.DEBT_TYP_CLASS, T2.CPA_TYPE, T2.CSP_NUMBER, T2.OB_ID, T2.CREATED_TMST, T2.LGA_IDENTIFIER, T2.LAD_NUMBER from CKT_OB_TYPE T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OBLIGATION T2 with(readuncommitted) on (@ladNumber = T2.LAD_NUMBER) and (@lgaIdentifier = T2.LGA_IDENTIFIER) and (T1.DEBT_TYP_ID = T2.DTY_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.CREATED_TMST <= @createdTmst) and ( T1.DEBT_TYP_CD in ('CRCH', 'CS', 'MS', 'AJ', 'MJ', 'MC') )
